<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouveau commentaire sur votre post</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 35px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .header .subtitle {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #495057;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .post-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #e8f0fe 100%);
            border-left: 4px solid #4285f4;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .post-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .post-content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 18px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #dadce0;
            color: #5f6368;
            font-style: italic;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            max-height: 180px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        .comment-info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
            border-left: 4px solid #0284c7;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .author-details {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 18px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0284c7;
            min-width: 90px;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #334155;
        }
        .comment-content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 22px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 2px solid #0ea5e9;
            color: #1e293b;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .footer .brand {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }
        .action-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            .post-title {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🔔 Nouveau commentaire sur votre post</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">ArtConnect Forum - Votre publication a reçu une réponse</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <!-- Informations sur le post -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="post-info">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <span class="icon">📋</span>
                        Informations sur votre post
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-title">{{ post_title }}</div>
                    <div class="post-content">{{ post_content }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Nouveau commentaire -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="comment-info">
                    <div class="section-title">
                        <span class="icon">💬</span>
                        Nouveau commentaire publié
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="author-details">
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Auteur :</span>
                            <span class="detail-value highlight">{{ comment_author_name }}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Email :</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{ comment_author_email }}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <span class="detail-label">Date :</span>
                            <span class="detail-value">{{ comment_date|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="comment-content">{{ comment_content|nl2br }}</div>
                    
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <a href="#" class="action-button">Voir sur le forum</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Message informatif -->
            <div style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 18px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 25px;">
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #92400e; font-size: 14px;">
                    <strong>💡 Conseil :</strong> Vous pouvez répondre directement à ce commentaire depuis la page du forum.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong class="brand">ArtConnect</strong> - Plateforme d'art communautaire</p>
            <p>Cet email a été généré automatiquement suite à un nouveau commentaire.</p>
            <p>Envoyé par {{ comment_author_name }} à {{ post_author_name }}</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11px; color: #adb5bd;">
                Pour ne plus recevoir ces notifications, contactez l'administrateur du site.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
